00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:17,288
l guess I've already told you
about my condition.

16
00:03:17,372 --> 00:03:19,999
Oh, well, only every time l see you.

17
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:31,678
- My car.
- This is your car.

18
00:03:31,761 --> 00:03:33,221
Oh, you're in a playful mood.

19
00:03:34,889 --> 00:03:38,685
- It's not good to make fun of a handicap.
