35
00:05:21,037 --> 00:05:23,206
How long have l been looking?

36
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:26,459
Find anything?

37
00:05:26,876 --> 00:05:28,878
Didn't think so.

38
00:05:28,962 --> 00:05:30,296
Let's go, huh?

39
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:32,757
Oh, fuck this.

40
00:05:33,883 --> 00:05:35,468
You're gonna pay for what you did.

41
00:05:36,302 --> 00:05:39,347
Beg forgiveness and then you pay.

42
00:05:43,059 --> 00:05:46,020
You don't have a clue, you freak!

43
00:05:46,104 --> 00:05:49,941
Beg my wife's forgiveness
before l blow your brains out.

44
00:05:50,024 --> 00:05:52,986
Leonard, you don't know what's going on.

45
00:05:53,069 --> 00:05:55,447
- You don't even know my name.
- Teddy.

46
00:05:55,530 --> 00:05:57,741
Cos you read it off a fucking picture.

47
00:05:57,824 --> 00:06:01,119
(breathless) You don't know who you are.

48
00:06:01,202 --> 00:06:05,749
- I'm Leonard Shelby from San Francisco.
- That's who you were. That's not...

49
00:06:05,832 --> 00:06:07,751
...what you've become.

50
00:06:07,834 --> 00:06:11,129
- Shut your mouth.
- You want to know, Lenny? Come on.

51
00:06:11,504 --> 00:06:13,548
Come on, let's go down to the basement.

52
00:06:13,631 --> 00:06:16,634
Let's go down, you and me together.

53
00:06:16,676 --> 00:06:19,804
